reviewText: I bought this on Amazon as a dvd, which I guess is not currently available, so I'm leaving a review for the VHS version.  I'm sure that I checked the reviews before I purchased this.  Well, anyway, this "workout" is absolutely AWFUL!!!  It looks like it was done in the 1970's or 80's.  It is ridiculously outdated and boring.  Please save your money and don't purchase this.
